      "title": "About \u2014 BrainDead",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# TRELLIS2 \u2014 Shape \u2192 Textured, Game-Ready Mesh\n\nImage \u2192 high-quality 3D with **CuMesh sharp-edge simplify** + full **PBR texture bake**.\n\n**Flow:** Load Image \u2192 Remove BG \u2192 Get Conditioning \u2192 Image-to-Shape \u2192 Shape-to-Textured-Mesh \u2192 **CuMesh Simplify** \u2192 **OVoxel Texture Bake** \u2192 textured mesh + diffuse/normal/metallic/roughness.\nThe bake re-projects PBR from the voxelgrid onto the decimated mesh, so you get a clean low-poly **textured** GLB (Export) + an interactive Preview 3D.\n\nModels (TRELLIS.2-4B) auto-download on first run. ~12\u201316GB VRAM.\n\n---\n**BrainDeadGuild** \u2014 created by **BizaNator**\n[BrainDeadGuild.com](https://BrainDeadGuild.com) \u00b7 [BrainDead.TV](https://BrainDead.TV) \u00b7 [GitHub](https://github.com/BizaNator/ComfyUI-BrainDead) \u00b7 [Discord](https://braindeadguild.com/discord)"
      ]
    },
